I"´<ol>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/security/limits.conf</code>:
```
    <ul>
      <li>soft nofile 64000</li>
      <li>hard nofile 64000
root soft nofile 64000
root hard nofile 64000
```</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/pam.d/common-session</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>...
session required pam_limits.so
...
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Edit <code class="highlighter-rouge">/etc/pam.d/common-session-noninteractive</code>:
    <div class="highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code>...
session required pam_limits.so
...
</code></pre></div>    </div>
  </li>
  <li>Reboot</li>
</ol>

